      "tool_title": "Fabrication Completion Notice",
      "activity_name": "Handover to Testing",
      "tier": "both",
      "notes": "Final tool in WB08. Confirms all fabrication travelers are signed off, all in-process QC checks passed, and the fabricated unit is ready for testing/QA phase. Sign-off sets projects.status = 'Testing Phase' and unlocks WB09.",
      "sections": [
        {
          "id": "s1",
